arbitres
Class Partie2Joueurs

java.lang.Object
  arbitres.Partie2Joueurs

public class Partie2Joueurs
extends Object

A referee for a two-players game :

  • Ask successively each player to play.
  • Look if the game is over.
  • Tells who is the winner.

Version:
$Revision: 1.0 $
